title: Al Jazeera America September 16, 2013 920AM EDT
description:
This is a test. Tell me if it works, I'll upload more of these.

This is an ISO file that I used Alcohol 120% to rip from original DVD recording.

It's in SD, standard definition, 4:3 aspect radio.

Al Jazeera America from 9:20 AM to 1:40 PM EDT on September 16, 2013.
There is coverage of the Washington DC Navy Yard shooting, and other news.
This is the new Al Jazeera America channel, I can't find it streaming anywhere.
 
The menu will say 8:20 AM, I am in the USA central time zone.

Let me know via comments if you can burn this to a DVD and watch it.

I have tons of these vids.

I will try and seed for a several hours each day, however I will probably only seed each file for thirty days.
 
Thank you for seeding, and thanks to Pirate Bay for all this. 

Leave any other comments below.
